    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Teudebertus">Teu&lt;tpertus></name></persName> filio
                            <persName>bone memorie <name ref="Romaldus">Rumualdi</name></persName>
                        permuta beni con <persName ref="#people/3309" key="#Bishops"
                            >Ambrosius</persName> gratia Dei huius sancte Lucane ecclesie humilis
                            <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> (…). Teutpertus cede ad parte ecclesie
                        vestre <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName> una petia de terra mea, quas abeo in loco <placeName
                            ref="#places/64"
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention #Roads"
                            >Asulari</placeName>, qui <rs key="#Confinia">uno caput</rs> tenet in
                            <rs key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention">terra
                            domni regi</rs>, alio caput tene in terra me quas mihi reservo, lato uno
                        tene in <rs key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention"
                            >terra domni regis</rs>, alio lato tene in terra que Riodaldo abere
                        videtur et in <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention">terra domni
                            regis</rs>; petia ipsa (…) quod est per mensura ad iuxta pertica <rs
                            key="#Size">sistariorum triginta duo</rs> (…). Riceve in cambio duo
                        petie de terra in predicto loco Asulari, pertinentes ipsius <rs
                            key="#Mother_churches">episcopatus</rs> vestri <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Confinia #Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, qui una ex ipse petie est tenente uno caput in <rs
                            key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, alio caput tene in terra <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Confinia #Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, quas mihi menime dedisti, ambas latera est tenente in
                        terra mea; et illa alia petia est tenente uno caput cum uno lato in <rs
                            key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, et aliquantulo in terra mea, alio caput
                        tene in terra <persName key="#Confinia"><name ref="Alchis"
                            >Alchisi</name></persName>, et alio lato tene in terra <persName
                            ref="#people/3307" key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions"
                            >Heriprandi</persName>; ambos petie (…) quod sunt per mensura ad iusta
                        pertica <rs key="#Size">sistariorum viginti quattuor</rs> (…), cum <rs
                            key="#Stone #Walls">petre et mura</rs> quas infra esse videtur in
                        integrum. Ubi et super hanc comutationem direxisti <rs
                            key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities">misso vestro</rs>, idest
                            <persName key="#Witness #Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Deacons"
                                ><name ref="Teuprandus">Teusprando</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diacono</rs> et <persName ref="#people/1514"
                            key="#Marquis/duke">Adalbertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> de sua parte direxit <rs
                            key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities">misso suo</rs>, idest
                            <persName key="#Witness #Missus_of_other_public_authorities"><name
                                ref="Odalbaldus">Odelpaldo</name></persName>, qui ambulaverunt et
                        previderunt hac renuntiaverunt qualiter melioratam comotationem (…). Pena in
                        duplum (…). <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Giselfredus"
                                >Ghiselfridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs key="#Commutatio"
                            >cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            key="#Mother_churches #Bishops">Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Oltre ai due missi sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>:
                            <persName key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Teofridus"
                            >Teufridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Notary"><name
                                ref="Andreas">Andreas</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Scabini">schabinus</rs>,
                                <persName><name ref="Samuel">Samuel</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Aregis">Aroghisi</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>quondam <name ref="Ghisi">Ghisi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ildebrandus">Hildiprandus</name></persName>
                        filio <persName>quondam <name ref="Ildefredus"
                        >Hiltifridi</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
